metrics_conclusion: Old Man has higher complexity than the average song  in terms Chord Complexity and Chord Progression Novelty.
key_conclusion: Old Man has sections analyzed in the following keys: D Dorian,  and D Mixolydian.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: The D Maj chords are borrowed from the Mixolydian mode.
Verse is in mode of D Dorian, not D Minor (Aeolian). Changes made to reflect the borrowed D Major chord is from the Mixolydian mode which the song alternates between.
